1
00:00:36,039 --> 00:00:37,079
Careful, everyone.

2
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:40,759
Come on.

3
00:00:42,759 --> 00:00:43,240
Slow down.

4
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:44,240
Here, give me a hand.

5
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:45,719
Easy now.

6
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,439
This looks like...

7
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:50,039
some kind of Ritual layout.

8
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,079
That's the Four Mindfulnesses,

9
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,719
the Four Right Efforts,

10
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:54,840
the Four Bases of Power.

11
00:00:57,719 --> 00:01:00,600
The north one is the Pure Five Faculties.

12
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:03,159
Where temples, pagodas, and demons stand,

13
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:06,079
chaotic thoughts and anger arise.

14
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,319
So the Nine-Story Pagoda

15
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:09,040
should be at the center of the energy field,

16
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,879
which is the lotus position in the north.

17
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:17,879
Come.

18
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,920
This is Qilian juniper.

19
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,159
Below are square and round timbers,

20
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:36,799
plus a rammed-earth structure.

21
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:38,319
Be careful when you go down there.

22
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:40,239
Don't damage the load-bearing logs below.

23
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,400
Get your gear ready. We're going down.

24
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,040
Okay.

25
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,599
Go get the rope.

26
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:13,360
What is this thing carved here?

27
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:17,319
A bull? A wolf? What is it?

28
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,520
A bull-wolf?

29
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,639
A donkey, maybe.

30
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,360
In The Scroll of the Heroic Lord Baoji's Triumphs,

31
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,599
the silver demon, the White Wolf King,

32
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,719
this must be it.

33
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,400
How do you know?

34
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,560
The Scroll of the Heroic Lord Baoji's Triumphs,

35
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:31,800
Dawang told me everything before he left.

36
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:36,919
I remember the White Wolf King's name was

37
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,599
something like Bingpo Zhenyu Shan.

38
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,719
Wait, hold on.

39
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:42,960
You've got me all confused.

40
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,120
Is it a wolf or a mountain?

41
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,080
How can you not understand anything?

42
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:50,360
This thing here, it's a wolf.

43
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,360
It looks like a bull,

44
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,800
but it's not called a bull-wolf.

45
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:55,360
Its name is Bingpo Zhenyu Shan.

46
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:57,319
A bit long, just deal with it.

47
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,120
Wait, it's a perfectly good wolf.

48
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,360
Why's it named after a mountain?

49
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:03,439
I've heard of this Bingpo Zhenyu Shan.

50
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:05,479
In life, it was a giant white wolf,

51
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,759
ancestor of all vicious wolves in Kunlun.

52
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,199
Legend says after it died,

53
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:11,439
it became a massive ice crystal mountain,

54
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:14,199
hence the name Bingpo Zhenyu Shan.

55
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:17,120
They say it guards the base of the pagoda,

56
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:19,240
protecting the gateway to Mengna Valley.

57
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,159
The moment anyone approaches,

58
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,599
the demon wolf descends from the sky

59
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,319
and devours everyone.

60
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,080
This ice disc

61
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,520
must be an ornament called a Ling Gai.

62
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,439
Probably every floor has one.

63
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,560
Only by opening this Ling Gai

64
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,039
can we enter the next level.

65
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:38,680
Wait.

66
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,719
It's open.

67
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,639
Push!

68
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,719
Look.

69
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:51,840
Look.

70
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,439
Old Lu, come take a look.

71
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,399
Come on.

72
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,279
Slow down, easy now.

73
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,920
Come, come, watch your legs.

74
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,800
You're so clumsy.

75
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:54,399
Hurry, take a look at this.

76
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,240
Impressive, isn't it?

77
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,160
After going down so many floors,

78
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,560
we finally see a proper relic.

79
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,519
You know what?

80
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,879
Coming down floor by floor so smoothly,

81
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,319
it actually makes me uneasy.

82
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,959
You're a glutton for punishment.

83
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,800
You just have to trigger a trap,

84
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,519
then have a near-death experience,

85
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,959
for you to feel at ease, right?

86
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:18,199
Old Lu, you've got it wrong there.

87
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:20,240
Fatty, that's an archaeologist's instinct.

88
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,879
Give him a break,

89
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,120
I'm getting nervous too.

90
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:23,560
This Nine-Story Pagoda

91
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,439
should be where an evil god is buried.

92
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,480
How could there be no defenses at all?

93
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:28,720
Brother Chen,

94
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,920
how's the situation down there?

95
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,879
Is it safe or not?

96
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,879
This floor is different from the others.

97
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:39,399
Ghost Banners are hanging everywhere.

98
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,480
A statue is where the Ling Gai should be.

99
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,519
For safety's sake, just stay up there.

100
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,720
Alright.

101
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,360
Be careful down there then.

102
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:52,879
Tell you what,

103
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:55,480
I'll send Bi Huaqiang down to help you.

104
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,639
Let me have a sip of water.

105
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,279
An Xiang.

106
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,120
Sit.

107
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:45,079
Are you

108
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:48,160
hiding something from me?

109
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,759
I'm not hiding anything from you.

110
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,079
It's just that I've noticed

111
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:01,160
you've gotten along well with them lately,

112
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:04,240
especially with that guy named Lu.

113
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,079
Did they

114
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,480
plan to ditch us and leave on their own

115
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:15,079
without giving you a heads-up?

116
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,759
How could they possibly tell me?

117
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,680
No matter how well we get along,

118
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,839
we've only just met, after all.

119
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,920
If they really had told me,

120
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,560
I'd definitely have told you.

121
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,759
These past few days,

122
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,800
I've been feeling awful.

123
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:53,040
About what happened to Aunt He,

124
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:59,040
I hope you don't overthink it.

125
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:03,000
Godfather, I understand.

126
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,759
Look at these Ghost Banners.

127
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:09,199
They kind of resemble a Ritual layout.

128
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,000
The directions marked here

129
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,319
are different from normal.

130
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:15,079
Our north is their west,

131
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:17,040
the red Xiniu Hezhou.

132
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,439
Our east is their north,

133
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,720
the blue Beiju Luzhou.

134
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,920
All this east, south, west, and north...

135
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,199
you've got me totally turned around.

136
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,439
I just want to know,

137
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:27,360
where is this floor's mechanism exactly?

138
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:29,399
Where on earth is the Ling Gai?

139
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:31,959
I think,

140
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,440
the Ling Gai was centered on past floors.

141
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,440
This time, if you ask me,

142
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:41,360
the Ling Gai must be under this statue.

143
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,840
The Ling Gai's definitely under it.

144
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,679
Let's move it aside.

145
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,519
What are you "hmm-ing" about?

146
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:49,799
Everything I say is based on evidence.

147
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,879
I examined this statue carefully.

148
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,879
Look at this.

149
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,399
On the surface, it looks kind and gentle,

150
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:57,000
but in fact,

151
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,600
it's cradling a human head in its arms.

152
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,600
What is this thing?

153
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,240
It's pretty strange, right?

154
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,320
So let's study it.

155
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,399
Alright, we'll follow your lead.

156
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,320
Forget everything else,

157
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,639
let's move it aside first.

158
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,000
Give me a hand.

159
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,519
Come on.

160
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,679
You broke it!

161
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,799
What's going on?

162
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,960
Chen Youxi, up ahead!

163
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,320
Take cover, quick!

164
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,200
Hurry, hurry, take cover!

165
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:27,759
Quick!

166
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,879
Don't just stand there!

167
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:30,720
Old White-hair, push it aside!

168
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,279
Then we can just head down, right?

169
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,600
It won't budge! This thing...

170
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:38,320
This statue must have a mechanism.

171
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,039
It can't be pushed open.

172
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,679
Look!

173
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,600
The color of those beads has changed.

174
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:43,120
When we first came in,

175
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,120
the directional colors were opposite,

176
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,080
they were reversed.

177
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,360
I, I have an idea.

178
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,399
Maybe,

179
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:52,879
if we restore the colors of these beads

180
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:54,120
back to their original state,

181
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,200
perhaps,

182
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,240
perhaps the mechanism will shut off.

183
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,440
Old Lu makes a good point.

184
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:00,759
Anyway,

185
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,200
you'll be the one turning the beads.

186
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:02,519
Okay, okay, okay.

187
00:10:02,519 --> 00:10:03,240
We'll cover you.

188
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,879
No, no, no!

189
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:07,440
I'm just the idea guy.

190
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:11,600
Should we go down and help them?

191
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:20,240
No need.

192
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,799
He can handle it.

193
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,200
Old Chen,

194
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:30,559
I noticed that

195
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:34,120
it only fires every three seconds.

196
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,399
Just like playing that Contra game.

197
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:38,559
There's a time gap in between.

198
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:39,840
Three seconds?

199
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,240
You're kidding me.

200
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:44,200
Three seconds won't cover a round trip.

201
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,679
Don't even try it!

202
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,759
If you mess up,

203
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,919
the arrows will shoot from behind,

204
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:50,200
and I'll be the first one skewered!

205
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,200
If I don't try,

206
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,639
the arrows will soon pierce the statue,

207
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,720
and shoot right through the front too.

208
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,320
Two, three.

209
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:59,080
One, two, three.

210
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,720
One, two, three.

211
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,759
Lend me the Demon-Subduing Umbrella.

212
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:10,879
One, two, three.

213
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:14,320
One, two, three.

214
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,279
One, two, three.

215
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:22,840
One, two, three.

216
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:27,480
Old Chen, the statue is almost sliced up!

217
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,600
I can't hold on much longer!

218
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,200
It stopped!

219
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,200
Move aside, let me see.

220
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:12,159
What did I tell you?

221
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:14,039
I said it was right under here.

222
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:14,879
Am I right or what?

223
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,000
Huaqiang.

224
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,799
This is a cultural relic.

225
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:18,919
This time,

226
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:20,360
we should at least

227
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,120
keep one of them intact.

228
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:05,519
Why are you causing trouble?

229
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:06,360
You're such a coward.

230
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,320
Bro,

231
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,960
you can't just scare people like that.

232
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,720
My heart nearly jumped out of my chest.

233
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:13,720
So this is the Bingpo Zhenyu Shan?

234
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:16,480
I thought there'd really be a wolf-headed,

235
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,720
human-bodied mummy here.

236
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:19,519
Turns out it's just a statue.

237
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,480
Don't look down on this statue.

238
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:26,159
Making something like this isn't cheap.

239
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:28,519
What's it made of?

240
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:34,879
It's ice crystal from the Nine-Story Pagoda.

241
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,480
But...

242
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,080
what I don't get is...

243
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,080
Look here.

244
00:13:39,279 --> 00:13:41,559
These layered, scale-like ripples,

245
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:42,919
what are they?

246
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:44,679
These...

247
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:47,000
Must be special sound waves sealed inside.

248
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:49,080
Once the ice crystal shatters,

249
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:51,320
it could trigger an avalanche.

250
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,559
Now I get it.

251
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:56,240
This is how it guards Mengna Valley's gate.

252
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:58,279
If an intruder breaks it,

253
00:13:58,279 --> 00:14:00,519
they'll be buried here by an avalanche.

254
00:14:00,559 --> 00:14:02,320
Forget about entering Mengna Valley.

255
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,240
I'm just wondering,

256
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,120
where exactly is the gate

257
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,320
to this Mengna Valley?

258
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:09,360
We just discussed this, and you still ask?

259
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:10,720
Use your head, would you?

260
00:14:10,759 --> 00:14:13,679
It's obviously buried under the mountain.

261
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:15,320
The Jueda people were really cunning.

262
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,879
They buried the gate to Mengna Valley

263
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,039
right down here.

264
00:14:18,039 --> 00:14:18,879
You can't move it,

265
00:14:18,879 --> 00:14:19,759
or push it,

266
00:14:19,759 --> 00:14:21,399
and breaking it causes an avalanche.

267
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,879
It's a brilliant dead end.

268
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,279
Won't budge.

269
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:33,879
Hey, Old White-hair,

270
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,639
this thing won't budge.

271
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,720
Isn't that obvious?

272
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,600
Then what do you suggest?

273
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,320
With so many of us here,

274
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,600
are we just going to stand and watch?

275
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,120
A little bug.

276
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:52,679
This little bug is pretty interesting.

277
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,159
In such a harsh environment,

278
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,799
it can still survive.

279
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,399
Mother Nature,

280
00:14:57,840 --> 00:15:00,279
can create all kinds of miracles.

281
00:15:00,279 --> 00:15:01,960
In this frozen environment,

282
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,200
to adapt,

283
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,480
it kept evolving,

284
00:15:04,519 --> 00:15:05,559
into something like this.

285
00:15:05,559 --> 00:15:06,919
Looks like a little ladybug.

286
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:08,559
Careful!

287
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:11,919
These bugs have lived here for years.

288
00:15:12,159 --> 00:15:12,960
Maybe

289
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,360
they're also part of the trap.

290
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,960
When I was a kid, I heard

291
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,960
that in the Kunlun Mountains,

292
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,440
there is a kind of blue bug.

293
00:15:19,039 --> 00:15:20,279
They come from hell,

294
00:15:20,559 --> 00:15:21,679
and whoever touches them

295
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,159
will face utter disaster.

296
00:15:25,399 --> 00:15:27,960
Stop spreading these feudal superstitions.

297
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,279
Hell? Utter disaster? Seriously?

298
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,279
Tian Qing, don't touch it!

